<section class="section section--tint body-why">
  <div class="container">

    <div class="body-why__head">
      <h2 class="body-why__heading">
        Why Choose Menon Medispa for Your Body Treatments &amp; Enhancements?
      </h2>
      <p class="body-why__intro">
        Our comprehensive approach integrates advanced wellness with medical-grade procedures to deliver transformative results that support your long-term health and confidence.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="body-why__layout">

      <div class="body-why__text-col">

        <div class="body-why__block">
          <h3 class="body-why__block-heading">Our Integrated Treatment Philosophy</h3>
          <p class="body-why__block-body">
            At Menon Medispa, we believe that true body wellness requires a holistic perspective. Each treatment is selected and customized not just for aesthetic outcomes, but to support your overall health. Our physician-led team evaluates your unique health profile, lifestyle, and goals to create a treatment plan that addresses root causes while delivering visible improvements.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="body-why__block">
          <h3 class="body-why__block-heading">What to Expect</h3>
          <p class="body-why__block-body">
            Your journey begins with a thorough consultation with Dr. Menon, who reviews your medical history and aesthetic goals before recommending any treatment. From there, every session is personalized to your progress and response, with follow-up care built into your treatment plan. We are committed to transparent communication, realistic expectations, and your long-term satisfaction.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .body-why .container {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .body-why__head {
    max-width: 820px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .body-why__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-h2);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .body-why__intro {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .body-why__layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
    align-items: start;
  }

  /* Accent-ruled text blocks */
  .body-why__text-col {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .body-why__block {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: var(--space-md);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-cta);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .body-why__block-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-subheading);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.25;
  }

  .body-why__block-body {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }
</style>
